Functions

expit <- function(x){
  num <- exp(x)
  denom <- 1+exp(x)
  return(num/denom)
}
pdf_normal <- function(y,kappa1,kappa2,log=FALSE){
  mu <- kappa1
  sigma2 <- kappa2
  if(log==FALSE){
    return(1/sqrt(2*pi*sigma2)*exp(-(y-mu)^2/(2*sigma2)))
  }
  else{
    return(-0.5*log(2*pi*sigma2)-(y-mu)^2/(2*sigma2))
  }
}
# Setting
# N set to 200 but can be easily changed to 100
T <- 750; N <- 200; MLE <- matrix(0,nrow=N,ncol=5); Median <- matrix(0,nrow=N,ncol=5); MSE <- matrix(0,nrow=N,ncol=5); SE <- matrix(0,nrow=N,ncol=5);
UB <- matrix(0,nrow=N,ncol=5); LB <- matrix(0,nrow=N,ncol=5); Length_CI <- matrix(0,nrow=N,ncol=5); cv <- abs(qnorm(0.5*(1-0.95))); count <- 1;
# True parameters
b0__ <- 1; b1__ <- 0.5; b2__ <- 0.3; c__ <- 0.1; m__ <- 0.7; 
true_par <- c(b0__,b1__,b2__,c__,m__);
# Initial guess
parameters <- c(-0.1,-1,-1,-0.75,1)
# Inference
while(count<(N+1)){
  set.seed(count*3)
  zt <- rnorm(T)
  sigma2 <- rep(0,T)
  sigma2[1] <- b0__/(1-b1__-b2__)
  for(j in 2:T){
    sigma2[j] <- b0__+b1__*sigma2[j-1]+b2__*sigma2[j-1]*(zt[j-1]-c__)^2
  }
  rt <- sqrt(sigma2)*zt+m__
  logLikeh2od <- function(theta){
  b0 <- exp(theta[1])
  b1 <- exp(theta[2])
  b2 <- exp(theta[3])
  c <- exp(theta[4])
  m <- theta[5]
  if((b2*(1+c^2)+b1)<1){
    sigma2_aux <- rep(0,T)
    sigma2_aux[1] <- b0/(1-b1-b2)
    for(k in 2:T){
      sigma2_aux[k] <- b0+b1*sigma2_aux[k-1]+b2*(rt[k-1]-m-c*sqrt(sigma2_aux[k-1]))^2
    }
    ll <- sum(pdf_normal(rt,m,sigma2_aux,TRUE))
    return(-ll)
  }
  else return(Inf)
  }
  # Optimisation
  optimisationResults <- ucminf(parameters,logLikeh2od,hessian = 2)
  estimate <- optimisationResults$par
  MLE[count,] <- c(exp(estimate[1]),exp(estimate[2]),exp(estimate[3]),exp(estimate[4]),estimate[5])
  # SE - Delta method
  helper_DM <- diag(optimisationResults$invhessian)
  SE[count,1:4] <-sqrt(helper_DM[1:4]*MLE[count,1:4]^2)
  SE[count,5] <- sqrt(helper_DM[5])
  UB[count,] <- MLE[count,]+cv*SE[count,]
  LB[count,] <- MLE[count,]-cv*SE[count,]
  MSE[count,] <- (MLE[count,]-true_par)^2
  Length_CI[count,] <- UB[count,]-LB[count,]
  count <- count+1
}
final_matrix <- cbind(colMeans(MLE),colMedians(MLE),colMeans(MSE),colMeans(SE),colMeans(Length_CI))
rownames_ <- c("b0_","b1_","b2_","c_","mu_")
row.names(final_matrix) <- rownames_
colnames_ <- c("Mean","Median","MSE","SE","Length C.I.")
row.names(final_matrix) <- rownames_
colnames(final_matrix) <- colnames_

#Comparison of rt__ and rt_fit
sigma2_fit <- rep(0,T)
MLE_fit <- as.numeric(final_matrix[,1])
sigma2_fit[1] <- MLE_fit[1]/(1-MLE_fit[2]-MLE_fit[3]*(1+MLE_fit[4])^2)
for(i in 2:T){
  sigma2_fit[i] <- MLE_fit[1]+MLE_fit[2]*sigma2_fit[i-1]+MLE_fit[3]*sigma2_fit[i-1]*(zt[i-1]-MLE_fit[4])^2
}
rt_fit <- sqrt(sigma2_fit)*zt+MLE_fit[5]
